#%Module1.0

module-whatis       "Amber is a suite of biomolecular simulation programs"
module-url          "https://ambermd.org"
module-license      "Non-commercial license"
module-maintainer   "João Pedro Agostinho de Sousa <joao.agostinho-de-sousa@psi.ch>"
module-help "
AMBER is a long-standing molecular dynamics (MD) software suite used to
simulate biomolecules such as proteins, nucleic acids, and protein-ligand
systems. It is common in academic and industry research groups working in drug
discovery, structural biology, and materials-adjacent biomolecular modeling.
"

# Version 26 requires cuda version <12.9
if { ${V_PKG} == "26" } {
  module switch cuda cuda/12.8.1
}

